title: SacraTrendo, CA 10/5: He's Back, Herro Snarl, Dune, J Balvin

description:
On this episode of SacraTrendo, CA Jack and DJ Danl discuss Trump coming back from the hospital totally chill and for sure totally okay, Tyler Herro gets his own snarl, Dune and Batman are getting pushed back, and J Balvin is next to have a collab with McDonalds.
